text: $6 for a few slices of ultra thin char Siew meat and pork. My first time and will avoid eating at this shop at all cost next time.

Bedok Cooked Food is back after a 3-year hiatus! Best char siew, roast pork and best roast duck ever! I only eat duck from this stall - no other can match it. The quality and tasting their food has not changed at all. If anything, the char siew has improved in flavour. I hope all their old customers will return to support them.
Rude hawker, horrible char siew. Not worth trying.
